Carry out singing:
	say "I quietly hummed a jaunty tune[if Thomas Hastings is visible and Hercule Poirot is visible]. Thomas[end if][if Hercule Poirot is visible] and Poirot hummed along[end if][if Thomas Hastings is visible and Hercule Poirot is visible] in harmony[end if][if Thomas Hastings is visible and Hercule Poirot is not visible] and Thomas hummed along with me[end if].".

