When play begins:
	now the story viewpoint is first person singular;
	now the story tense is past tense;
	now the command prompt is "[bold type]>[roman type] [paragraph break]          [italic type][bracket]press any key[close bracket][roman type]";
	say "[bold type]Foreword[roman type]
[line break]by Captain Arthur Hastings, O.B.E. 
[line break]
[line break]     It has very nearly been thirty years since I was wounded on the Somme[unicode 8212]in the war which to me will always be the Great War[unicode 8212]and travelled to Styles St. Mary to finish my convalescence. It was there, by fateful serendipity, that I renewed my friendship with the man who first ignited my interest in detection. The famous Hercule Poirot![paragraph break]          >>>[command prompt]";
	wait for any key;
	now the command prompt is "[bold type]> [roman type]";
	say "[line break][line break]     I have already put pen to paper many a time in these past decades to chronicle my adventures with Poirot, throughout our extended cohabitation as well as during my visits from the Argentine where I eventually established myself after marriage. Most of these manuscripts have gone to print and are well-known nowadays to lovers of mystery and intrigue. What I have kept from the press, however, is the details of my family's repatriation and the profound impact it has had on all of our lives. With my friend's blessing I have therefore tried my hand at a more mundane kind of story to share with our entourage, relating a peaceful but memorable Sunday in the spring of 1939.[paragraph break]          >>>[command prompt]";
	wait for any key;
	say "[line break][line break]      The lodgings described herein have mercifully survived the Blitz and the subsequent years of conflict[unicode 8212]it is my hope that days such as this one will become commonplace once more as we reclaim our comfortable routines.[paragraph break]          >>>[command prompt]";
	wait for any key;
	now the objective is "choose a tie (1/8)";
	now the intro is seen;
	continue the action.
	
